headline: ManpowerGroup Talent Solutions Named a Global RPO Leader by Everest Group for 15th Consecutive Year
summary: ManpowerGroup Talent Solutions, a global leader in workforce solutions and part of the ManpowerGroup (NYSE: MAN) family of brands, has been named a Leader in Recruitment Process Outsourcing (RPO) for the 15th consecutive year in Everest Group's 2025 PEAK Matrix® Assessment. This milestone reflects sustained investments in AI-powered technologies, data-driven insights, and expert advisory services that help clients navigate today's dynamic talent landscape.

headline: O.C. Tanner Named Rewards and Recognition Leader by Leading Research Firm, Everest Group
summary: SALT LAKE CITY, June 26, 2025--O.C. Tanner, the global authority in employee recognition and workplace culture solutions, is honored to be recognized as a Leader in the 2025 Everest Group Rewards and Recognition (R&R) Solutions PEAK Matrix® Assessment. This prestigious designation underscores O.C. Tanner’s industry leadership, innovation, and unwavering commitment to helping organizations build cultures of appreciation through world-class recognition solutions.
